{"tid":294952,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"行 會 通 過 取 消 強 積 金 對 沖 方 案","createTime":"2017-06-23T11:32:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-24T14:20:21.000Z","uid":20933,"like":2,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fa8c0355d781ff50f9d147dcd8178ded444bb33e","tid":294952,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T11:32:01.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】行政會議下午召開特別會議，通過取消強積金對沖原方案。<br />\n<br />\n行政會議召開特別會議後，通過政府原方案全面取消強積金對沖，遣散費及長期服務金在實施日劃線，無追朔期，並設有十年過渡期。<br />\n<br />\n政府會預留79億資助僱主，而遣散費及長服金的計算比例將由月薪三分二降至二分一。<br />\n<br />\n會後行政長官梁振英和政務司司長張建宗指，分析過不同建議後認為原方案最可行，希望勞方及資方繼續聚焦討論，但強調下屆政府有權作出任何更改。"},{"pid":"7223c74ea044b4895f8ffc29c99d470cbb7cc573","tid":294952,"uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T11:32:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=225929\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D225929&d=Ro5gOZb4XY7tmuB7x%2FjLCjQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=e44ef3d2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D225929&h=9efa87fd\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=225929</a>"},{"pid":"363779c7f2414320b0bac5a2e95e1e8aea8dd2c3","tid":294952,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T11:33:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">而遣散費及長服金的計算比例將由月薪三分二降至二分一。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f64758c91cb63f8b63fb5f4d8d80ad46b5ef8c03","tid":294952,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T11:36:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8674e0e7b5bb36fda1e7a948a9ef825debc8d2f","tid":294952,"uid":5133,"like":1,"disli